HEPATITIS A, STRAWBERRIES - USA (04)
====================================
[1]
Date: Mon, 7 Apr 1997 05:14:16 -0400
From: Luiz Jacintho da Silva <luisjs@correionet.com.br>
Subject: Re: PRO/EDR> Hepatitis A, strawberries - USA (03)
All information concerning this outbreak assumes from the beginning that the
strawberries suffered contamination during some step of its processing in
the San Diego plant. Details concerning the preparation of the end products,
i.e. the fruit cups, served in the two Michigan schools are not available.
It is impossible to bring forward any reasonable explanation without further
information.
